data.description: Horse set up deluxe. Log horse barn w/loft, tack room, automatic heated waters on 5 acres of pasture. New perimeter fence with steel, horse holding area new wood post and wood plank. Beautiful private back yard with deck to two french doors off kitchen area. Home has new (1 year old) metal roof. Nice 'rancher' look to the whole deal.
